
Base URL : https://opensource-demo.orangehrmlive.com/web/index.php/auth/login

Test Cases
----------
1.	Login Test Case with valid credential:
•	Open the OrangeHRM login page.
•	Enter valid credentials.
•	Click the login button.
•	Verify successful login by checking the dashboard page title.
•	Logout the user.


2.	Invalid Login Test Case (with invalid credential):
•	Open the OrangeHRM login page.
•	Enter invalid credentials.
•	Click the login button.
•	Verify that an error message is displayed indicating invalid credentials.


3.	Add Employee Test Case:
•	Login to OrangeHRM.
•	Navigate to the "PIM" menu and select "Add Employee".
•	Fill in the required details (e.g., first name, last name).
•	Click the save button.
•	Verify that the employee is successfully added by checking the employee list for Personal Details.
•	Logout the user.


4.	Search Employee Test Case By Name:
•	Login to OrangeHRM.
•	Navigate to the "PIM" menu and select "Employee List".
•	Enter search criteria (e.g., employee name, employee ID).
•	Click the search button.
•	Verify that the record is found.
•	Logout the user.

5.	Search Employee Test Case By Id:
•	Login to OrangeHRM.
•	Navigate to the "PIM" menu and select "Employee List".
•	Enter search criteria (i.e employee ID).
•	Click the search button.
•	Verify employee id in search result.
•	Logout the user.


